# Component Decomposition Rule

- Keep page components focused on composition and routing concerns.
- Extract reusable UI blocks into separate files under `src/components/...`.
- Move pure data aggregation/formatting logic into utility modules instead of embedding it in JSX-heavy files.
- Prefer one component per file when a block has its own props, internal logic, or can be reused.
- For dashboard-like pages, split cards/panels into separate components by responsibility.

